          "trait_date": "2025-11-21T16:18:42.8526463+03:00",
          "locale_text": "\"Что ж, я узнал достаточно. Ступай\".",
          "speaker": "",
          "speaker_gender": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "enGB",
      "text": "\"I suppose I have heard enough. Go.\"",
